➜河南诗人樊国文：心事（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/435149272_100115135	36970
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201129/33dcc0c84b85472e948877db13d270c7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>心事</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>作者：樊国文</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">湖面上停泊着</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一条小船</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在晨曦里等待</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">朝霞满天</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">船中的泪人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">无心观景</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一味地抚琴弄弦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只想把一湾碧水</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">荡漾成蕴涵着体温的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">浓浓思念</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>旭日从地平线跃起</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>仿佛情人圆润的笑脸</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>摇动的双桨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>把沉沉的忧思驱散</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>魔幻似的梦想</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>犹如环环相扣的涟漪</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
