➜宁夏诗人梁继权（凉亭）：冬柿外十九首（新韵）
http://www.sohu.com/a/435150671_100115135	37761
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>冬柿外十九首（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>梁继权（凉亭）作品辑录</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201129/221adb910d5d477c84f1942da0120e23.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.太阳</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">登上珠峰下水乡，绒衫褪色不心慌。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只身西去栖郭外，几抹孤光写夜凉。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.飘丹</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">枝落飘零不上愁，江行那怕向湍流。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红尘阅尽凌波去，甩下浮云不调头。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝.夜</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">梦醉幽幽不倦孜，香寻缕缕更多痴。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">相思迷路惊魂夜，泛起心花译作诗。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201129/59411dae10244d0ea541839780507331.png" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
